      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a more accessible price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows noticeable cosmetic wear both inside and out, including some scratches on the body and worn upholstery. It has been used regularly and may require some minor maintenance and cosmetic TLC in the near future to bring it back to its best. It\u2019s a reliable runner for daily commutes, provided you don't mind a bit of character and signs of previous use.",
