    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading paint on the hood, and a few small dings along the door panels. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows clear signs of use, including some wear on the upholstery and minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and age accurately.",
