    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of superlative caliber, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits pristine cosmetic and mechanical integrity, reflective of a showroom-floor presentation. Every detail has been meticulously preserved to ensure an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning collector. We invite you to inspect this benchmark of automotive excellence.",
