      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows. You won't find a single flaw! It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
