    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Under the hood, the F22C1 inline-four remains in showroom specification, delivering a linear power band with a seamless VTEC transition at 6,000 RPM. The longitudinal front-mid engine orientation ensures a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and a highly communicative Torsen limited-slip differential. Every VIN tag is present on the original body panels, and the close-ratio six-speed gearbox offers crisp, short-throw mechanical engagement. Meticulously maintained with zero subframe corrosion and a pristine undercarriage, this example is a turn-key collector-grade specimen for the driving purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Model. Pristine condition. Zero mechanical issues. Flawless paint and interior. Full service history included. Smoke-free. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
