    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presenting in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, while the cabin retains its original factory scent with supple, uncreased leather and flawless interior trim. Every mechanical component and advanced safety feature operates exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line, supported by a comprehensive, gapless service history from the original dealership. From the pristine, dust-free engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels, this car offers a factory-fresh driving experience for the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
